simple_step: provides a collection of software components for
controlling stepper motors via USB. simple_step consists of three main
software componets:

1. firmware for the Atmel at90usb1287 microcontroller providing
   position and velocity control for stepper motors via clock and
   direction commands. 

2. a python api enabing communication with the at90usb1287
   microntroller via USB.

3. a command line interface which enables stepper motor control from the
   command line. 


Installation instructions can be found in the INSTALL file.


Author: William Dickson

